The Social Patriots advocate full support for Schleicher’s chancellorship and his rearmament program, believing that only through strength can Germany break free from the chains of Versailles and reclaim its rightful lands.

Schleicher, predictably, is pleased with our acceptance of this new political current—but his influence within our party is growing alarmingly fast. Perhaps too fast.

